<i>noun</i>: 완화 [완ː화], 경감 [경감] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>완화 [완ː화]</dt><br>
<dd>1. relaxation; easing</dd><br>
<dd>긴장된 상태나 매우 급한 것을 느슨하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of relaxing something tense or stressful.</dd><br>
<dd>2. relief; alleviation</dd><br>
<dd>병의 증상이 약해짐.</dd><br>
<dd>For the symptoms of a disease to be assuaged.</dd><br>
<dt>경감 [경감]</dt><br>
<dd>alleviation; reduction</dd><br>
<dd>부담이나 고통 등을 덜어서 가볍게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of lessening and lightening a burden, pain, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>